description: Reconstruction of up to 100  Palestinian Homes in the West Bank

subproject.corporate outcome: Expansion and access to financial services for the poor, employment and income generation and access to markets, goods and services.
subproject.description: This project will construct 100 housing units in the West Bank for those families who have had their homes destroyed. The houses will be approximately 100 to 130 square meters and the beneficirias will be selected based upon a socio-economic criteria.
subproject.gender code: Gender equality as a significant objective
